narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course to anyone interested in psychology as it's presented in the public eye, not necessarily as actually practiced.
Excellent class in a discussion and presentation setting. Very interesting course material for anyone with the slightest interest in psychology, psychiatry, or the sciences in general
